{"tid":1854603,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】俄羅斯首現確診病例 意大利宣佈全國進入緊急狀態","createTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T15:00:49.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c0e3f033c849fe3a50ab6adab2ed677c3e12e65","tid":1854603,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:39:35.000Z","msg":"【21:54】意大利確診首兩宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎個案後，總理孔特宣布該國進入緊急狀態，撥款500萬歐元應對疫情。緊急狀態將維持6個月。<br />\n<br />\n【21:32】俄羅斯有兩名中國公民確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎，是俄國首次有確診病例。兩宗個案分別在俄國秋明市，以及與中國接壤的外貝加爾邊疆區確診。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200131/s00005/1580434441813/【武漢肺炎】俄羅斯首現確診病例-意大利頒布緊急狀態\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200131%2Fs00005%2F1580434441813%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E9%A0%92%E5%B8%83%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=1c135b86\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2Farticle%2F20200131%2Fs00005%2F1580434441813%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E9%A0%92%E5%B8%83%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E7%8B%80%E6%85%8B&h=7d0d4af1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/國際/article/20200131/s00005/1580434441813/【武漢肺炎】俄羅斯首現確診病例-意大利頒布緊急狀態</a>"},{"pid":"057e94360d0c6fa28f0b53d8cd947ec56aad2199","tid":1854603,"uid":178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:42:08.000Z","msg":"Who cares WHO?!"},{"pid":"e336914b08dad153e16dbceb07d7a815a02e9498","tid":1854603,"uid":33437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"中國逼到意大利進入緊急狀態<br />\n又贏， 不戰而屈人之兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ado